title: Southern Lehigh's Nina DeLuna talks about winning 2nd straight district tennis title (VIDEO)
text:
By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 12, 2015 10:41 PM, updated October 12, 2015 10:57 PM 
Southern Lehigh 's Nina DeLuna won her second straight District 11 Class AAA tennis title on Monday at Lehigh University. 
The junior earned a 6-4, 6-2 win over Easton 's Elessa Jacobs in the final. 
See what DeLuna had to say after the match in the video at the top of this post.
